#Installing NCBI BLAST+ package
##11/15/2019
##/Users/amberleighhenschen/GithubRepos/Learning-Bioinformatics/IntroductionToBlast/03_NCBIBlast


I am installing the BLAST+ package so that I can run BLAST commands on my command line following the instructions found at https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK52640/.


Steps:

```
#Downloaded BLAST+ executable file from ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast/executables/LATEST/.
ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast/executables/LATEST/ncbi-blast-2.9.0+-x64-macosx.tar.gz

#Installed package
tar zxvpf ncbi-blast-2.9.0+-x64-macosx.tar.gz

#Configured installed package
export PATH=$PATH:/Users/amberleighhenschen/GithubRepos/Learning-Bioinformatics/IntroductionToBlast/03_NCBIBlast/bin
```

This process has installed and configured the BLAST+ package so I can use the BLAST commands locally.

Note: Be sure to name files and folders using appropriate formats. No spaces or special characters except underscores.
